{"title":"Mac OS下安装和配置Maven","date":"2020-05-11T14:52:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年5月11日","L":"2020/05/11","MM-DD":"05-11"},"link":"2020/05/macos-maven","categories":["Java"],"updated":"2020-09-19T16:09:31.404Z","content":"<h3 id=\"1.-下载maven\">1. 下载Maven<a title=\"#1.-下载maven\" href=\"#1.-下载maven\"></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>打开Maven官方下载网页：<a href=\"http://maven.apache.org/download.cgi\" target=\"_blank\">http://maven.apache.org/download.cgi</a></p>\n<img src=\"https://images.shiguangping.com/imgs/20200511145456.png\" alt=\"image-20200511145456074\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" />\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>解压下载的压缩包放到自己喜欢的目录下，<em>（放到一个固定的目录，不要随意改动）</em></p>\n<p>比如：/Users/liyan/Documents/CodeRepositorise/apache-maven-3.6.3</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.shiguangping.com/imgs/20200511150127.png\" alt=\"image-20200511150127552\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"2.-配置环境变量\">2. 配置环境变量<a title=\"#2.-配置环境变量\" href=\"#2.-配置环境变量\"></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>打开终端，输入一下命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">open ~/.bash_profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>打开.bash_profile文件，添加环境变量：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">export M2_HOME&#x3D;&#x2F;Users&#x2F;liyan&#x2F;Documents&#x2F;CodeRepositorise&#x2F;apache-maven-3.6.3</span><br><span class=\"line\">export PATH&#x3D;$PATH:$M2_HOME&#x2F;bin </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.shiguangping.com/imgs/20200511150521.png\" alt=\"image-20200511150521799\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p>添加好之后保存并退出，执行下面的命令使配置生效：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">source ~/.bash_profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"3.-查看配置是否生效\">3. 查看配置是否生效<a title=\"#3.-查看配置是否生效\" href=\"#3.-查看配置是否生效\"></a></h3>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>在终端输入命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mvn -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://images.shiguangping.com/imgs/20200511150731.png\" alt=\"image-20200511150731453\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<p><em><strong>到这里，Maven配置成功</strong></em></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n","prev":{"title":"IDEA中的Web项目移动到Eclipse","link":"2020/06/ideaproj-to-eclipse"},"next":{"title":"设置eclipse格式化时不对注释进行格式化","link":"2020/04/eclipse-format-code"},"plink":"https://www.shiguangping.com/2020/05/macos-maven/","toc":[{"id":"1.-下载maven","title":"1. 下载Maven","index":"1"},{"id":"2.-配置环境变量","title":"2. 配置环境变量","index":"2"},{"id":"3.-查看配置是否生效","title":"3. 查看配置是否生效","index":"3"}]}